data.description: This exquisite residence graces a superb location, nestled within a serene cul-de-sac in the charming Bonita neighborhood. Boasting an expansive layout of 7 bedrooms and 5 bathrooms, this home is complemented by a generous lot adorned with a pool and spa. The backyard offers an inviting oasis for both hosting gatherings and unwinding during the sun-drenched summer days. Parking convenience is ensured by the three-car garage, which also offers abundant storage provisions. The community exudes a family-friendly ambiance and enjoys proximity to schools, parks, and shopping establishments. Beyond its inviting boundaries, seamless commuting to downtown San Diego and the beach is effortlessly attainable. This residence is an ideal haven for larger families or those seeking a capacious abode enriched with an array of amenities.
